name: Lil Garlic
description:
Rude Veggies is a collection of 10 radical characters, inspired in the vegetables lovers and my childhood imagination. Full of colors, funny outfits, cool hobbies and tons of good vibes!

Lil Garlic, is the 3rd character, a very anxious vegetable, with a sophisticated watch which he is always staring at, waiting for amazing things to happen, for example: Finding new collectors! 

He is ready to meet you!


Drawing by MNNLLIA
2021
